      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 11:12:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国将完善金融业监管机制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/china-to-improve-supervision-mechanism-for-finance-industry</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据中国共产党对世界第二大经济体的长期规划，中国将完善对 66 万亿美元金融业的监管机制，规范各种金融活动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/china-to-improve-supervision-mechanism-for-finance-industry</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 10:56:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>习近平誓言重塑中国财政，帮助负债累累的地方</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/xi-vows-more-local-government-support-in-new-economic-blueprint</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国执政党共产党公布了针对世界第二大经济体的长期蓝图，国家主席习近平也公布了旨在提振中国负债累累的地方政府财政的全面计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/xi-vows-more-local-government-support-in-new-economic-blueprint</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 09:13:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马来西亚拦截新加坡失踪油轮 起火</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/malaysia-intercepts-missing-oil-tanker-from-singapore-fire</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马来西亚海事当局称，一艘从新加坡以东发生碰撞起火的油轮于周日凌晨在马来西亚沿海被拦截。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/malaysia-intercepts-missing-oil-tanker-from-singapore-fire</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 08:41:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>丹格特因涉嫌垄断放弃钢铁投资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/dangote-to-scrap-steel-investment-over-allegations-of-monopoly</link>
      <description><![CDATA[非洲首富阿里科·丹格特取消了在尼日利亚投资新钢铁厂的计划，此前尼日利亚政府指责他试图利用在西非国家新建的炼油厂垄断市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/dangote-to-scrap-steel-investment-over-allegations-of-monopoly</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 07:34:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贝利的沉默引发英国央行 8 月降息悬念</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/bailey-s-silent-treatment-stokes-boe-august-rate-cut-suspense</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国央行行长安德鲁·贝利（Andrew Bailey）已经沉默了两个月，这让每个人都无法猜测利率将何时发生重大变化，也没有太多可参考的信息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/bailey-s-silent-treatment-stokes-boe-august-rate-cut-suspense</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哥伦比亚石油公司寻求立法降低租金和电价</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-20/colombian-president-asks-lawmakers-law-change-to-lower-electricity-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哥伦比亚总统古斯塔沃·佩特罗表示，哥伦比亚的电价和租金是通货膨胀的主要驱动因素，政府希望立法者修改规范此类成本的立法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-20/colombian-president-asks-lawmakers-law-change-to-lower-electricity-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 20 Jul 2024 23:46:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
